  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下工业物联网的数据流向。核心是从执行器控制器开始，经过遥测数据流，最终回到另一个执行器控制器的闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点是ActuatorController。我注意到您提到\"另一个\"执行器控制器，意味着流程中有两个ActuatorController节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，首尾各一个。中间需要经过EdgeNode做边缘计算，再到PLC_Logic进行逻辑控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出四个主要节点：起始的ActuatorController、TelemetryStream、EdgeNode、PLC_Logic。连线关系是串行的对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "串行没错，但别忘了最后还要连到第二个ActuatorController形成闭环。目前你只画了四个，还缺终点那个。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已补充，现在五个节点形成完整链条：ActuatorController → TelemetryStream → EdgeNode → PLC_Logic → ActuatorController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "EdgeNode到PLC_Logic的箭头方向确认一下，数据是从边缘节点下发到PLC，不是反向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认方向是EdgeNode指向PLC_Logic，符合边缘层向控制层下发的逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "另外，两个ActuatorController虽然类型相同，但职能不同：第一个是采集触发端，第二个是执行响应端，建议用不同标识区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，起点标记为a，终点标记为e，中间b、c、d依次对应TelemetryStream、EdgeNode、PLC_Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚注意到PLC_Logic到第二个ActuatorController的连线好像没显示？这个控制指令下发很关键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修复，补充了d到e的连线。现在完整流程是：a采集→b传输→c边缘处理→d逻辑控制→e执行，闭环确认无误。",
      "elements_involved": [
